ext":"就是执念，有什么不可以？","id":18,"figure":["avg_300_phenxi_1",6]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_300_phenxi_1#7$1","id":19},{"type":"dialogue","name":"菲亚梅塔","text":"没有道理也好，于事无补也好，徒劳无功也好，我打定了主意要做，我就会去做！","id":20,"figure":["avg_300_phenxi_1",6]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_300_phenxi_1#7$1","id":21},{"type":"dialogue","name":"菲亚梅塔","text":"你以为我们是为了什么战斗？","id":22,"figure":["avg_300_phenxi_1",6]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_300_phenxi_1#2$1","id":23},{"type":"dialogue","name":"菲亚梅塔","text":"你以为你念的那些经，那些让人发昏的长篇大论，把你自己都绕得云里雾里的胡话——不是你的执念吗？","id":24,"figure":["avg_300_phenxi_1",1]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_300_phenxi_1#2$1","id":25},{"type":"dialogue","name":"菲亚梅塔","text":"你，我，每个人，谁不是为了执念站在这里？","id":26,"figure":["avg_300_phenxi_1",1]},{"type":"dialog","id":27},{"type":"character","id":28},{"type":"playsound","key":"$p_atk_rifle_s","id":29},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":30},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"1","g":"1","b":"1","fadetime":"0.3","block":"true","id":31},{"type":"character","id":32},{"type":"image","xScale":"1","yScale":"1","id":33},{"type":"imagetween","xScaleTo":"0.8","yScaleTo":"0.8","duration":"20","block":"false","id":34},{"type":"playsound","key":"$swordtsing1","volume":"1","id":35},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","fadetime":"1.5","block":"false","id":36},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.3","xstrength":"10","ystrength":"12","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"true","id":37},{"type":"dialog","id":38},{"type":"text","text":"铳响破空而来。","id":39},{"type":"text","text":"只是瞄准的对象并非安多恩。","id":40},{"type":"text","text":"猝不及防，他感到手中的铳脱手而去。","id":41},{"type":"dialog","id":42},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":43},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":44},{"type":"character","id":45},{"type":"image","id":46},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":47},{"type":"text","text":"他突然觉得这样很好。","id":48},{"type":"text","text":"他的铳会留在拉特兰。","id":49},{"type":"text","text":"或许他永远不会说，但是——谁能不喜爱拉特兰？","id":50},{"type":"text","text":"那些安宁的日子、喜悦的时光、快乐的瞬间......","id":51},{"type":"text","text":"为了这份“喜爱”，他曾愧悔，负疚，羞耻，怀疑。","id":52},{"type":"text","text":"或许他永远没办法做一个天生的拉特兰人。","id":53},{"type":"text","text":"但在这一刻，当想到他的铳将会留在这里，在这个念头冒出来的一刻。","id":54},{"type":"text","text":"在面前的人怒视他的这一瞬。","id":55},{"type":"text","text":"那种安宁又如气泡一般浮出水面，小小地炸开一朵几不可见的水花。","id":56},{"type":"text","text":"他曾经在信与疑的道路上跋涉万里。","id":57},{"type":"text","text":"离开这一条路，再离开下一条路。","id":58},{"type":"text","text":"他以为他行于荒野，失去自己的根系。","id":59},{"type":"text","text":"但也许并非如此。","id":60},{"type":"text","text":"在许多事情上，都并非如此。","id":61},{"type":"text","text":"他轻轻道了一声感谢。","id":62},{"type":"text","text":"过往未来，时间与空间的所有历史中，没有人会听到这声感谢。","id":63},{"type":"text","text":"但已经足够。","id":64},{"type":"dialog","id":65},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":66},{"type":"character","name":"avg_213_mostma_1#7$1","id":67},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莫斯提马","text":"终于来了吗，我还以为你睡着了。","id":68,"figure":["avg_213_mostma_1",6]},{"type":"dialog","id":69},{"type":"character","id":70},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_transmissionget","id":71},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":72},{"type":"dialogue","name":"蕾缪安","text":"体谅体谅我吧，合适的狙击位置很难找的。","id":73},{"type":"character","name":"avg_300_phenxi_1#7$1","id":74},{"type":"dialogue","name":"菲亚梅塔","text":"行了，安多恩，束手......","id":75,"figure":["avg_300_phenxi_1",6]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_351_1#2$1","id":76},{"type":"dialogue","name":"安多恩","text":"（低声）为了执念......站在这里......","id":77,"figure":["avg_npc_351_1",1]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_213_mostma_1#3$1","id":78},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莫斯提马","text":"小心！","id":79,"figure":["avg_213_mostma_1",2]},{"type":"character","id":80},{"type":"dialog","id":81},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_351_1#6$1","id":82},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"1.7","xstrength":"20","ystrength":"40","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"f