我们所做的一切，不是为了得救......","id":109,"figure":["avg_npc_351_1",7]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_351_1#8$1","id":110},{"type":"dialogue","name":"安多恩","text":"而是为了有资格成为自己的拯救者。","id":111,"figure":["avg_npc_351_1",7]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_300_phenxi_1#1$1","id":112},{"type":"dialogue","name":"菲亚梅塔","text":"清醒了，安多恩？那就抬起头直面我——刚才的战斗简直是在向一截木桩挥拳。","id":113,"figure":["avg_300_phenxi_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_351_1#2$1","id":114},{"type":"dialogue","name":"安多恩","text":"我将行我的道。不论这是不是它赋予我的使命......","id":115,"figure":["avg_npc_351_1",1]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_351_1#1$1","id":116},{"type":"dialogue","name":"安多恩","text":"我也要谢谢你，菲亚梅塔。","id":117,"figure":["avg_npc_351_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_300_phenxi_1#7$1","id":118},{"type":"dialogue","name":"菲亚梅塔","text":"不客气，在你的葬礼上，我会把你的大彻大悟转告给你那些朋友们的。","id":119,"figure":["avg_300_phenxi_1",6]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_300_phenxi_1#7$1","id":120},{"type":"dialogue","name":"菲亚梅塔","text":"至于现在，你还是——","id":121,"figure":["avg_300_phenxi_1",6]},{"type":"character","id":122},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"可惜可惜，现在还不是时候，这家伙对我还有用呢。","id":123},{"type":"dialog","id":124},{"type":"playsound","key":"$grenade_launcher_shot","id":125},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":126},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"1","ystrength":"40","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":127},{"type":"playsound","key":"$grenade_explosion","id":128},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_sp_ballista","id":129},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":130},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"0.05","block":"true","id":131},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"0.05","block":"true","id":132},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"0.05","block":"true","id":133},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":134},{