_npc_351_1#6$1","id":164},{"type":"dialogue","name":"安多恩","text":"无论在哪里相会，希望我们都依然紧攥住那一点执念。","id":165,"figure":["avg_npc_351_1",5]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_351_1#6$1","id":166},{"type":"dialogue","name":"安多恩","text":"正如你说的，我们因这些执念而存在。","id":167,"figure":["avg_npc_351_1",5]},{"type":"dialog","id":168},{"type":"character","id":169},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"1","ystrength":"40","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":170},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_sp_ballista","id":171},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":172},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"0.05","block":"true","id":173},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"0.05","block":"true","id":174},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"0.05","block":"true","id":175},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"1","block":"false","id":176},{"type":"dialog","id":177},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":178},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":179},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":180},{"type":"character","id":181},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/c/c5/Avg_bg_26_g9_laterano_street.png","screenadapt":"showall","id":182},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":183},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$drift_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act9d0d0/m_avg_drift_loop.mp3","volume":"0.4","id":184,"musicid":1},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":185},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_367_1#1$1","id":186},{"type":"dialogue","name":"焦急的酒店经理","text":"小姐，您这样我们很难办的。","id":187,"figure":["avg_npc_367_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_367_1#1$1","id":188},{"type":"dialogue","name":"焦急的酒店经理","text":"能不能先从我们大楼的招牌上下来？您要再这样我就得联系戍卫队了！","id":189,"figure":["avg_npc_367_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_367_1#1$1","id":190},{"type":"dialogue","name":"焦急的酒店经理","text":"不过，虽说是题外话，我真的很好奇——","id":191,"figure":["avg_npc_367_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_367_1#1$1","id":192},{"type":"dialogue","name":"焦急的酒店经理","text":"您是怎么把轮椅弄上去的？","id":193,"figure":["avg_npc_367_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_353_1#10$1","id":194},{"type":"dialogue","name":"蕾缪安","text":"总有些办法。","id":195,"figure":["avg_npc_353_1",9]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_367_1#1$1","id":196},{"type":"dialogue","name":"焦急的酒店经理","text":"远处的烟尘......又有爆炸吗？最近的爆炸是不是也太多了一点......说是开会，简直像是过节。","id":197,"figure":["avg_npc_367_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_353_1#9$1","id":198},{"type":"dialogue","name":"蕾缪安","text":"姑娘，虽然很抱歉......能来帮我一把吗？","id":199,"figure":["avg_npc_353_1",8]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_353_1#10$1","id":200},{"type":"dialogue","name":"蕾缪安","text":"啊哈哈，有时候登上高处简单，下来就不那么容易了呢。","id":201,"figure":["avg_npc_353_1",9]},{"type":"dialog","id":202},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":203},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":204},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":205},{"type":"character","id":206},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/c/c0/Avg_bg_26_g2_laterano_cathedralhall.png","screenadapt":"showall","id":207},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":208},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":209},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":210},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$ponder_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act15d0d0/m_avg_ponder_loop.mp3","volume":"0.4","id":211,"musicid":2},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_222","id":212},{"type":"dialogue","name":"愤慨的使节","text":"开什么玩笑，我必须质疑拉特兰的管理能力，并要求一个合理的解释！那帮危险分子搞出来的爆炸震坏了我的收藏！","id":213,"figure":"avg_npc_222"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_165","id":214},{"type":"dialogue","name":"局促的使节","text":"听说拉特兰的启示圣钟时隔千年再度鸣响了？是教宗阁下为了欢迎我们到来特意安排的吗？","id":215,"figure":"avg_npc_165"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_175","id":216},{"type":"dialogue","name":"迟疑的使节","text":"说真的，我简直无法忍受和这些野蛮人共处一室。若不是看在教宗阁下的面子上......","id":217,"figure":"avg_npc_175"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_176","id":218},{"type":"dialogue","name":"文雅的使节","text":"让我们带来的厨子做好饭等我们回去，我不打算参加第二次拉特兰的晚宴。","id":219,"figure":"avg_npc_176"},{"type":"dialog","id":220},{"type":"character","id":221},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","id":222},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_361_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_356_1#9$1","fadetime":"1","id":223},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":224},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_361_1#1$1","id":225},{"type":"dialogue","name":"薇尔丽芙","text":"凭这些人......真的能带来哪怕一丝改变？大部分人只是投机分子......甚至投机分子都算好的。","id":226,"figure":["avg_npc_361_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_356_1#1$1","id":227},{"type":"dialogue","name":"教宗","text":"能。这件事只有拉特兰可以做，也只有拉特兰适合做。因为拉特兰是奇迹之城，因为拉特兰永远公允。","id":228,"figure":["avg_npc_356_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_361_1#4$1","id":229},{"type":"dialogue","name":"薇尔丽芙","text":"教宗阁下......我将为我们祝祷。","id":230,"figure":["avg_npc_361_1",3]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_356_1#9$1","id":231},{"type":"dialogue","name":"教宗","text":"难得见你这么紧张，薇尔。","id":232,"figure":["avg_npc_356_1",8]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_356_1#9$1","id":233},{"type":"dialogue","name":"教宗","text":"我年纪大了，也不会什么了不起的把戏了，只能是迈开老腿走到黑。","id":234,"figure":["avg_npc_356_1",8]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_369_1#1$1","id":235},{"type":"dialogue","name":"修士","text":"教宗阁下，短波广播转播的设备架设完成了。","id":236,"figure":["avg_npc_369_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_356_1#10$1","id":237},{"type":"dialogue","name":"教宗","text":"谢谢你。","id":238,"figure":["avg_npc_356_1",9]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_356_1#2$1","id":239},{"type":"dialogue","name":"教宗","text":"愿我不负所承袭的圣徒之名。","id":240,"figure":["avg_npc_356_1",1]},{"type":"dialog","id":241},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":242},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":243},{"type":"character","id":244},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/c/c0/Avg_bg_26_g2_laterano_cathedralhall.png","screenadapt":"showall","id":245},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":246},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":247},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_356_1#1$1","id":248},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伊万杰利斯塔十一世","text":"来自泰拉诸国的使者，伊万杰利斯塔十一世向你们致意。","id":249,"figure":["avg_npc_356_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_356_1#1$1","id":250},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伊万杰利斯塔十一世","text":"我们正面临挑战，不是拉特兰，而是泰拉的每一个国家。","id":251,"figure":["avg_npc_356_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_356_1#1$1","id":252},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伊万杰利斯塔十一世","text":"如各位所知，今日的泰拉诸国建筑在移动城市的轮毂之上。这并不仅为对现实景象的描述。","id":253,"figure":["avg_npc_356_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_356_1#1$1","id":254},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伊万杰利斯塔十一世","text":"“现代国家”的概念，伴随着移动城市的诞生而奠定。","id":255,"figure":["avg_npc_356_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_356_1#2$1","id":256},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伊万杰利斯塔十一世","text":"曾经，“国家”仅为聚落，拥有共同生活方式之人在天灾肆虐下聚结成“国”，国界即为大多数人视野的边界。","id":257,"figure":["avg_npc_356_1",1]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_356_1#2$1","id":258},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伊万杰利斯塔十一世","text":"移动城市的诞生改变了国家。","id":259,"figure":["avg_npc_356_1",1]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_356_1#1$1","id":260},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伊万杰利斯塔十一世","text":"如诸人一般，国家与国家交流愈密，摩擦渐生。","id":261,"figure":["avg_npc_356_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_356_1#1$1","id":262},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伊万杰利斯塔十一世","text":"“摩擦”，我似乎不该用如此轻缓的词汇简括历史。","id":263,"figure":["avg_npc_356_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_356_1#6$1","id":264},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伊万杰利斯塔十一世","text":"我亲眼目睹高卢的陨落。","id":265,"figure":["avg_npc_356_1",5]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_356_1#6$1","id":266},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伊万杰利斯塔十一世","text":"辉煌的“世界之都”毁于一夕，咆哮的装甲战舰嘶哑沉寂，所向披靡的高卢老近卫军化为焚火与硝烟。","id":267,"figure":["avg_npc_356_1",5]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_356_1#6$1","id":268},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伊万杰利斯塔十一世","text":"为这场陨落付出代价的不止高卢，还有文明。","id":269,"figure":["avg_npc_356_1",5]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_356_1#6$1","id":270},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伊万杰利斯塔十一世","text":"那位“高卢人的皇帝”与他的无畏军团甚至无法让一个雄踞大地中央的帝国存续。","id":271,"figure":["avg_npc_356_1",5]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_356_1#8$1","id":272},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伊万杰利斯塔十一世","text":"——那什么才能维护泰拉人在天灾摧残下胼手胝足编织积攒的文明？","id":273,"figure":["avg_npc_356_1",7]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_356_1#2$1","id":274},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伊万杰利斯塔十一世","text":"拉特兰人曾为了那场席卷大陆的战争奔走，穿越荒野与王廷的信使为拉特兰赢得了信用与声誉。","id":275,"figure":["avg_npc_356_1",1]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伊万杰利斯塔十一世","text":"萨科塔听到每个国家声称渴望安宁与和平。","id":276,"figure":["avg_npc_356_1",1]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_356_1#1$1","id":277},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伊万杰利斯塔十一世","text":"然而世人亦见到太多花色不一的“和平”在城堡、宫廷与营帐的角落里捏塑成型。","id":278,"figure":["avg_npc_356_1",0]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伊万杰利斯塔十一世","text":"一些利于部分人的秘密于此缔结，然后在预想不到的时刻倾塌崩毁，颠覆国家的安宁。","id":279,"figure":["avg_npc_356_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_356_1#1$1","id":280},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伊万杰利斯塔十一世","text":"我们已久未见横扫大陆的征服与扩张，但诸色默契或交易却在众人目力所及之外左右国家与人的命运。","id":281,"figure":["avg_npc_356_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_356_1#1$1","id":282},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伊万杰利斯塔十一世","text":"今日，启示已然降临。","id":283,"figure":["avg_npc_356_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_356_1#1$1","id":284},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伊万杰利斯塔十一世","text":"我的愿望是，和平缔造的过程一旦开始便要经受考察，少数人的秘密默契当被诸国摒弃。","id":285,"figure":["avg_npc_356_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_356_1#1$1","id":286},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伊万杰利斯塔十一世","text":"每一位思想不再留恋于过去时代、关心这片大地前途的人，都应该考虑这样一些问题——","id":287,"figure":["avg_npc_356_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_356_1#2$1","id":288},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伊万杰利斯塔十一世","text":"我们的文明如何得以延续？","id":289,"figure":["avg_npc_356_1",1]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_356_1#2$1","id":290},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伊万杰利斯塔十一世","text":"对于和平的挑战究竟是对多少人的挑战？","id":291,"figure":["avg_npc_356_1",1]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_356_1#2$1","id":292},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伊万杰利斯塔十一世","text":"一个国家的安全意味着多少国家的安全？","id":293,"figure":["avg_npc_356_1",1]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_356_1#1$1","id":294},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伊万杰利斯塔十一世","text":"在这片大地，生存系于文明。除非安宁能及于他人，否则安宁也不能独施于我。","id":295,"figure":["avg_npc_356_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_356_1#1$1","id":296},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伊万杰利斯塔十一世","text":"我呼吁，根据共同的约定，建立这样一个协议实体，目的在于使诸国共同获得安全的相互保证。","id":297,"figure":["avg_npc_356_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_356_1#10$1","id":298},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伊万杰利斯塔十一世","text":"我们在利害安危上的关联远比许多人想象得更加紧密。","id":299,"figure":["avg_npc_356_1",9]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_356_1#10$1","id":300},{"type":"dialogue","name":"伊万杰利斯塔十一世","text":"泰拉应并肩生存到底。","id":301,"figure":["avg_npc_356_1",9]},{"type":"character","id":302},{"type":"dialog","id":303},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":304},{"type":"subtitle","text":"伊万杰利斯塔十一世于1099年3月18日发表的讲演被后世称为“拉特兰主张”，著录于每一版《万国峰会手册》的第一页。","x":"300","y":"370","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"700","id":305},{"type":"subtitle","id":306},{"type":"dialog","id":307},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"3","id":308},{"type":"dialog","id":309},{"type":"character","id":310},{"type":"image","id":311}],"characters":["安多恩","菲亚梅塔","莫斯提马","蕾缪安","？？？","奥伦","薇尔丽芙","焦急的酒店经理","愤慨的使节","局促的使节","迟疑的使节","文雅的使节","教宗","修士","伊万杰利斯塔十一世"]}